1. Order Creation Integration (/store/useStore.ts)
typescript
// Record inventory movements for each cart item
for (const cartItem of cart) {
  await get().recordInventoryMovement({
    productId: cartItem.id,
    type: 'sale',
    quantity: -cartItem.quantity, // Negative for sales
    referenceId: order.id,
  });
}
When orders are created:

Automatically records inventory movements for all cart items
Uses 'sale' type with negative quantities
Links to order ID for tracking
Updates local product stock levels
